snippet.title: Minecraft with RTX Beta Available Now | Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Minecraft with RTX Beta for Windows 10 is available now!
Learn More: https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/geforce/news/minecraft-with-rtx-beta-out-now-download-play
 
Download today to experience new levels of realism and immersion with real-time ray tracing and NVIDIA DLSS 2.0 in the world’s most popular game. 
 
Subscribe to GeForce! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCL-g3eGJi1omSDSz48AML-g/featured
